        <item>
            <title>【評測】ROG Zephyrus G16 輕薄電競筆電，再見厚底勁嘈風扇，超薄寧靜機內置 RTX 4070</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/25/rog-zephyrus-g16/notebook/notebook-review/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rog-zephyrus-g16</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/25/rog-zephyrus-g16/notebook/notebook-review/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Ultrabook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[筆電測試]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[asus]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Game Pass]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gaming laptop]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[pc game]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG Zephyrus G16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1282990</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以前講到電競手提電腦，好多朋友都會聯想到超厚底機身，重量大到不可能帶出街，而且在打機時風扇需要發出轟音維持散熱。今次我們要睇的華碩最新 ROG Zephyrus G16 系列，就打破了以往電競手提電腦又厚又重的定律，融合輕薄設計與效能，搭載 AMD Ryzen AI 9 HX 370 處理器，並配備 RTX 40 系列顯示卡，機身厚度只有 14.9mm（最薄部份），重量也只有 1.85 kg。筆電兼備 16 吋 OLED 熒幕，以及和機面背光燈設計，極之適合追求流動打機暢快感受的朋友仔，當然也適合需要隨時隨地帶住強大電腦外出工作的創作者朋友。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283033 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04408-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04408-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04408.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283022 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04429-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04429-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04429.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ROG Zephyrus G16 擁有高效處理器與影像處理器，但給用家超薄超輕機身</p><h2>輕薄設計與高效能完美結合</h2><p>ROG Zephyrus G16 GA605W 以鋁合金材質製作，機身通過 CNC 精密加工，維持輕薄便攜。筆電提供「日蝕灰」與「鉑月銀」兩種配色，重量僅約 1.85 公斤，最薄位置厚度只有 14.9mm，而最厚處也只厚 16.9 mm。特別的是手提電腦搭配的 200W 變壓器，同樣比以往的電競手提電腦細好多，電腦再加火牛的總重量約，為 2.4 kg，適合長時間攜帶，或者拿去旅行工幹，隨時隨地打機。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283030 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04406-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04406-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04406.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283032 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04409-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04409-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04409.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1283024 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04388-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04388-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04388.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電腦跟來的變壓器比同類型電腦細得多，只有約一部 iPhone Pro Max 的大小</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1283025 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04389-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04389-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04389.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲變壓器連電線整體重量也只約為 600g</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1283026 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04390-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04390-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04390.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而電腦本身則只重約 1800g，為一部輕盈電競手提電腦</p><p>機身上蓋引入了「Slash 燈效」，簡單來説就是比較沉實的燈光條，以多個 LED 燈所組成。它支援 15 種自訂燈光模式。無論在電腦運作以至休眠時，都可發出閃燈效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283028 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04402-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04402-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04402.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283029 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04401-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04401-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04401.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283034 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04439-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04439-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04439.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>打開機蓋後你即刻會看到面積大得驚人的觸控板。它長闊分別為 15cm x 10cm，比上代觸控板面積提升 37%，可説是專門為創意工作者度身訂造。在户外工作例如需要放大相片，檢視影片，這個大型觸控板都可令操作更得心應手。不過留意它實體有 click 感的點擊按鈕的部份為下半部，而上半部都可以輕觸式點擊操作電腦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283020 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04463-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04463-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04463.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電腦最薄處距離桌面只有約 1.65cm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283066 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04458-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04458-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04458.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以前意想不到電競手提電腦都可以這麼薄</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1283019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04471-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04471-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04471.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></p><p>鍵盤的部份也合符遊戲玩家以至辦公用家的工作需要，鍵帽尺寸增大 12% 之外，即使在這麼薄的機身這部 GA605W 也配置了 RGB 背光燈設計。右上角配備玻璃材質電源鍵，開機那一刻開始已感受到貼身的操作感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283067 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04432-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04432-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04432.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲連電源鍵的手感都十分考究</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283060 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04415-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04415-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04415.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配備 RGB 背光鍵盤</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283061 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04410-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04410-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04410.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲極大面積觸控板帶來靈活電腦操作感</p><h2><span lang="EN-US">ROG Intelligent Cooling (</span>智能散熱技術<span lang="EN-US">) </span>改善遊戲速度與風扇噪音平衡</h2><p>ROG Zephyrus G16 機內的應用程式，利用 AI 協助電腦為用家提升效能。它可細緻調整 CPU 與 GPU 的頻率，以及在風扇的效率，讓用家在極需要處理效能時，能發揮電腦的最佳表現之餘，而同時可控制散熱系統，獲得更寧靜的使用體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283004 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241218213455-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241218213455-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241218213455.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283040 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04383-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04383-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04383.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而在一間底噪為 45dB 的房間中，電腦全速運作時噪音也只升到約 58dB，可説是不太嘈吵的音量，在電競手提電腦來説表現相當不錯</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283013 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04446-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04446-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04446.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲經過智能調節，在不完全運作的情況下，可減低風扇噪音</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
