            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年摺機賣到成行成市，花款亦愈來愈多，令大家看到眼花瞭亂。但其實一部電話花款及功能再多，一般人實際使用時也只是用來影相、上網揾料、打機……簡單來説就是講求實用性。HUAWEI 最近就在香港推出 HUAWEI Mate X6 這部全新「大摺」，究竟使用起來感受如何？就讓我們為大家分享一下用後體驗吧。</p><h2>相關影片 :</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_49946"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YGSR-e4rPJQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>超輕薄唔玩花巧實用先行</h2><p>今次 HUAWEI 推出的 Mate X6「大摺」，可説是繼承了上代港行「大摺」HUAWEI Mate X3 的設計 ID：大玩纖巧輕薄，重量只有 239g，攤開使用時機身厚度只有 5mm 左右，即使摺疊起來厚度也只是 10mm，加上邊位採用微弧設計，拿上手完全不覺刮手，輕薄設計亦令大家摺疊時單手握機使用都無問題，而攤開以大熒幕使用，雙手長時間拿著手機也不會容易感到疲累，手感十分不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_46huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_46huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_46huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 HUAWEI 推出的 HUAWEI Mate X6「大摺」，外形與上代港行「大摺」HUAWEI Mate X3 相比可説是擁有相同設計 ID。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_20huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_20huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_20huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身依然十分薄身，摺疊起來時機身厚度只是 10mm。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_23huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_23huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_23huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而展開機身使用時機身厚度更薄至只有 5mm 左右，超級薄身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283158" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_03huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_03huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_03huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這個纖巧設計，令大家拿 HUAWEI Mate X6 外出使用時十分輕鬆，長時間雙手拿機也不會易感疲倦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_41huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_41huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_41huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配色方面，HUAWEI Mate X6 設有 3 種設計，分別是採用素皮機背的寰宇紅及曜石黑，以及採用織錦纖維物料機背的星雲灰。</p><p>除了纖巧之餘，HUAWEI Mate X6 亦設有內外兩塊大尺寸的 OLED 熒幕，摺疊時可以使用機面的 6.45 吋熒幕，大家可以見到邊框十分窄，用盡所有空間；而攤開手機就可以透過 7.93 吋摺疊式 OLED 熒幕使用手機，感覺就像一部小型平板，令大家可以在更廣闊熒幕上進行不同工作，甚至同時使用多個程式，提升多工作業效率。（這部分後文會再作詳述。）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_12huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_12huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_12huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身支援 IPX8 抗水功能，使用時更安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_10huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_10huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_10huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機內亦搭配了 2000W/m．K 超高導熱石墨烯 3D 液冷 VC 立體散熱結構，散熱表現有一定保證。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
